title: Dekoboko Nymphomania
description:
A collection of oneshots.

Chapter One: Imagine, that the roles of whales and humans were swapped. So whales (or whale-like creatures) would be rather small, able to talk and smart. Humans would be large, stupid and hunted by whale-people.

Chapter Two: A girl finally visits her boyfriend's parents at their house. For some bizarre reason, every appliance is made of human bodies. When the girls realizes that she too will be turned into an appliance, she attempts to escape her destiny by having sex . . .
